         !text "It turned out to be the toughest case of"
         !text "your detective career. Clues have led to"
         !text "nothing but dead ends. Nobody is        "
         !text "talking. Meanwhile, the crime boss you  "
         !text "are after is still operating from       "
         !text "somewhere. You're about to throw in the "
         !text "towel.                                  "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "But wait! Something breaks. You trail a "
         !text "stooge of the crime organization to a   "
         !text "cheap, seedy hotel, hoping to pump some "
         !text "answers out of him. You break into the  "
         !text "hotel room and, with the butt end of    "
         !text "your trusty .44 magnum, you knock him   "
         !text "cold.                                   "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "This could be the lead you've waited    "
         !text "for. Now if you could find some clues..."
